<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pedido confirmado — Tá na Mão!</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    body{font-family:"Outfit",sans-serif;background:#f4f6f4;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px}
    .box{background:#fff;max-width:500px;width:100%;padding:40px 32px;border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.08);text-align:center}
    .icon{font-size:3.5em;margin-bottom:16px}
    h1{color:#3C6E47;font-size:1.6em;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px}
    p{color:#666;font-size:0.95em;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:24px}
    a{display:inline-block;background:#C9A86A;color:#2D5235;font-weight:800;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:50px;text-decoration:none;font-size:1em;transition:all 0.2s}
    a:hover{background:#d6b77c;transform:translateY(-2px)}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="icon">✅</div>
    <h1>Pedido confirmado!</h1>
    <p>Seu pagamento foi aprovado com sucesso.<br>Em breve entraremos em contato para combinar a entrega. Fique de olho no WhatsApp!</p>
    <a href="/TanaMao/">Fazer outro pedido</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
